renz must be used concomitantly with retinoids that undergo metabolism by CYP450 3A4.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/96287/', '', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Simeprevir, Cabotegravir, Zanamivir, Velpatasvir, Rilpivirine, Dolutegravir, More', 'Pertuzumab, Tisagenlecleucel, Aminolevulinic acid, Omacetaxine mepesuccinate, Altretamine, Enasidenib, Mitotane, Niraparib, Selinexor, Aflibercept, Trastuzumab, More', 1767369485);
